{"tid":1166473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺學校唔見咗USB，去左保安室等失物，見到有個中國學生報失一部華為電話","createTime":"2019-05-22T12:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T16:01:09.000Z","uid":109923,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fb5952cfbca8dc83b5f3c8cc8c20f6ef4c45e6","tid":1166473,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"嗰位中國學生報稱喺宿舍common遺失華為電話，要求睇cctv，但係啲實Q似乎唔多想幫...<br />\n<br />\n實Q哥哥：check CCTV要報左警先可以睇，唔可以隨便睇<br />\n<br />\n實Q阿頭：不如你返宿舍再搵下，問下人有冇見過先啦<br />\n<br />\n擾攘咗一陣，仲搞到舍監都黎埋，最後都決定睇閉路電視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來部電話俾清潔姐姐掃咗落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個中國學生衝咗去垃圾房搵電話"},{"pid":"a4297de7df1ad6ce72a1c930048975ab15f338f3","tid":1166473,"uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"連一向貪心既清潔工都不屌華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceffa6f4bc3923eca188daea228b0f9031513973","tid":1166473,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6c1ddfc9cc3f5617b1cc0e7cec4bf0c6d348ac","tid":1166473,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"尊才"},{"pid":"539ee68a7db43fd820de52aa5739707e87928cb0","tid":1166473,"uid":61954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a5aedf84a45322b57f0453eb04f3c864692755","tid":1166473,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:49:41.000Z","msg":"連清潔姐姐 都